name: Jabba's Twerps
Lore: '''Look, Jabba, next time you want to see me, come see me yourself. Don''t send one of these twerps.''',
Text: 'If opponent just initiated battle where your alien leader is present, deploy up to three non-unique aliens to that location from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. OR Once per game, retrieve 1 Force for each of your alien leaders present at any battleground sites.',
